main event: A woman in Lynn, Massachusetts spotted a bright, disc-shaped object with a rotating red light hovering over the nearby woods in May 1965.
interesting points: The object was approximately 150 feet above the ground and was observed for several minutes before suddenly shooting straight up at an incredible speed.
A man driving in Lynn, Massachusetts also reported seeing a large, round object with pulsating white light and flashing red and green lights on the periphery in May 1965.
The object remained stationary for about 2 minutes before accelerating rapidly and disappearing in a northeasterly direction.
The witness, who had considerable experience observing aircraft, stated this was unlike any conventional flying object he had ever seen.
